<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>FAQ — BK Vilona AI</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Frequently asked questions about BK Vilona AI — video creation, pricing, payments, referrals, and account management.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    :root {
      --bg: #0a0a1a; --bg2: #111127; --card: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); --accent: #00d9ff; --accent2: #00ff88;
      --grad: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d9ff, #00ff88);
      --text: #fff; --dim: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); overflow-x: hidden; line-height: 1.6; }
    .container { max-width: 860px; width: 100%; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; box-sizing: border-box; }
    nav { position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; background: rgba(10,10,26,0.9); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .nav-inner { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 16px 20px; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .logo { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; background: var(--grad); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: center; }
    .nav-links a { color: var(--dim); text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; transition: color .2s; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }
    .btn-nav { background: rgba(0,217,255,0.12); color: #00d9ff; border: 1px solid rgba(0,217,255,0.25); padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; transition: all .25s; }
    .btn-nav:hover { background: rgba(0,217,255,0.2); transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,217,255,0.15); }

    /* Hero */
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 64px 20px 48px; background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(0,217,255,0.08), transparent 50%); }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .hero h1 span { background: var(--grad); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
    .hero p { font-size: 16px; color: var(--dim); max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; }

    /* FAQ */
    .faq-section { padding: 16px 0 80px; }
    .faq-category { margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .faq-category-title {
      font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 16px; padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .accordion { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
    .accordion-item { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; overflow: hidden; transition: border-color .2s; }
    .accordion-item:hover { border-color: rgba(0,217,255,0.2); }
    .accordion-item.open { border-color: rgba(0,217,255,0.3); }
    .accordion-btn {
      width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      padding: 18px 20px; background: transparent; border: none; cursor: pointer;
      text-align: left; color: var(--text); font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; gap: 12px; transition: background .2s;
    }
    .accordion-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }
    .accordion-icon {
      flex-shrink: 0; width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(0,217,255,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(0,217,255,0.2);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 14px; color: var(--accent); transition: transform .25s, background .2s;
    }
    .accordion-item.open .accordion-icon { transform: rotate(45deg); background: rgba(0,217,255,0.2); }
    .accordion-body { display: none; padding: 0 20px 18px; font-size: 14px; color: var(--dim); line-height: 1.75; }
    .accordion-item.open .accordion-body { display: block; }
    .accordion-body code { background: rgba(0,217,255,0.1); color: var(--accent); padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 13px; }
    .accordion-body ul { padding-left: 18px; margin: 8px 0; }
    .accordion-body ul li { margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .accordion-body a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
    .accordion-body a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .highlight-box { background: rgba(0,255,136,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,136,0.15); border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 16px; margin-top: 10px; font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }
    .highlight-box strong { color: var(--accent2); }

    footer { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; color: var(--dim); font-size: 14px; }
    footer a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }

    @media(max-width: 640px) {
      .hero { padding: 48px 16px 32px; }
      .accordion-btn { font-size: 14px; padding: 14px 16px; }
      .accordion-body { padding: 0 16px 14px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a class="logo" href="/">BK Vilona AI</a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/faq" style="color:var(--text)">FAQ</a>
      <a href="/app" class="btn-nav">Open App</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Frequently Asked <span>Questions</span></h1>
    <p>Everything you need to know about BK Vilona AI — video creation, pricing, payments, and more.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="faq-section">
  <div class="container">

    <!-- How to Create Videos -->
    <div class="faq-category">
      <div class="faq-category-title">Creating Videos</div>
      <div class="accordion">

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-btn" onclick="toggle(this)">
            How do I create a video?
            <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            There are two ways to get started:
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Telegram Bot:</strong> Open the bot and type <code>/create</code>. Follow the step-by-step wizard — choose a niche, style, duration, and upload a product photo. The bot guides you through each step.</li>
              <li><strong>Web App:</strong> Go to <a href="/app">/app</a>, log in with Telegram, and click <strong>Create Video</strong> from the dashboard. You'll get the same wizard in a browser interface.</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="highlight-box"><strong>Tip:</strong> First-time users receive 1 free trial video — no payment needed.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-btn" onclick="toggle(this)">
            What types of videos can I make?
            <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            BK Vilona AI supports several video types:
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Standard Video</strong> — AI-generated promotional video from a single product photo (up to 60s)</li>
              <li><strong>Image Set Video</strong> — multi-scene video from up to 7 generated images</li>
              <li><strong>Talking Photo</strong> — animate a face/avatar to speak custom dialogue</li>
              <li><strong>Custom Duration</strong> — set any length from 5s up to 120s (Pro mode)</li>
            </ul>
            Choose your video type during the create flow.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-btn" onclick="toggle(this)">
            How long does video generation take?
            <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Most videos are ready in <strong>1–3 minutes</strong>. Longer videos (60s+) or image-set videos may take up to 5 minutes. You'll receive a Telegram notification the moment your video is done — you don't need to wait in the app.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-btn" onclick="toggle(this)">
            Can I customize the scenes and script?
            <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Yes. When creating a video, select <strong>Pro Mode</strong> to review and edit each scene prompt before generation. You can rewrite individual scene descriptions, adjust timing, and preview the full storyboard. The HPAS framework (Hook → Problem → Agitate → Solution) structures scenes automatically if you skip manual editing.
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Pricing -->
    <div class="faq-category">
      <div class="faq-category-title">Pricing &amp; Credits</div>
      <div class="accordion">

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-btn" onclick="toggle(this)">
            How does the credit system work?
            <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Credits are the currency used inside BK Vilona AI. <strong>1 Credit = 10 Units</strong> internally. Each video type costs a different number of credits based on length and complexity:
            <ul>
              <li>Short video (5–15s): ~5–10 credits</li>
              <li>Standard video (30s): ~20–30 credits</li>
              <li>Long video (60s): ~50–60 credits</li>
              <li>Image Set video: ~40–60 credits</li>
              <li>Talking Photo: ~15–25 credits</li>
            </ul>
            The exact cost is shown before you confirm each generation.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-btn" onclick="toggle(this)">
            Where can I buy credits?
            <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Use the <code>/topup</code> command in the bot or go to <strong>Billing</strong> in the web app. Available packages are shown with price and credit amounts. Select a package and choose your preferred payment method to proceed.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-btn" onclick="toggle(this)">
            Are there subscription plans?
            <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Yes. Monthly and annual subscription plans give you a recurring credit allowance at a discounted rate compared to one-time top-ups. Unused subscription credits roll over to the next billing cycle (up to 2× your monthly allowance). You can see available plans in the Billing section.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-btn" onclick="toggle(this)">
            What happens if video generation fails?
            <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            If your video fails to generate after all retry attempts, your credits are automatically refunded to your account. You'll receive a notification in Telegram with details. You can then try again or contact support if the issue persists.
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Payment Methods -->
    <div class="faq-category">
      <div class="faq-category-title">Payment Methods</div>
      <div class="accordion">

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-btn" onclick="toggle(this)">
            What payment methods are accepted?
            <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            BK Vilona AI supports multiple payment gateways:
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Midtrans</strong> — Bank transfer (BCA, BRI, Mandiri, BNI), GoPay, OVO, DANA, ShopeePay, and credit/debit cards</li>
              <li><strong>DuitKu</strong> — Indonesian virtual accounts and e-wallets</li>
              <li><strong>Tripay</strong> — Additional Indonesian payment channels</li>
              <li><strong>NOWPayments</strong> — Cryptocurrency (Bitcoin, USDT, ETH, and others)</li>
              <li><strong>Telegram Stars</strong> — Pay directly with Telegram Stars in the bot</li>
            </ul>
            Available methods may vary. The payment page shows only currently active gateways.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-btn" onclick="toggle(this)">
            How long does payment confirmation take?
            <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Most payments are confirmed instantly (e-wallet, virtual account). Bank transfers may take up to a few minutes. Crypto payments are confirmed after the required number of blockchain confirmations (typically 1–15 minutes). Credits are added to your account as soon as payment is confirmed.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-btn" onclick="toggle(this)">
            Is my payment information secure?
            <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Yes. All payments are processed through licensed third-party gateways (Midtrans, DuitKu, etc.). BK Vilona AI never stores your card or bank credentials — you enter payment details directly on the gateway's secure page.
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Referral Program -->
    <div class="faq-category">
      <div class="faq-category-title">Referral Program</div>
      <div class="accordion">

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-btn" onclick="toggle(this)">
            How does the referral program work?
            <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Share your personal referral link with friends. When someone signs up using your link and makes their first purchase, you earn a referral bonus in credits. Use the <code>/referral</code> command in the bot to get your unique link and see your referral stats.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-btn" onclick="toggle(this)">
            How much can I earn from referrals?
            <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            You earn a percentage of each referred user's top-up as credits. The current rate is shown in the <code>/referral</code> menu. There is no cap on referral earnings — the more users you refer, the more you earn.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-btn" onclick="toggle(this)">
            Can I cash out referral earnings?
            <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Yes. Once your referral balance reaches the minimum withdrawal threshold, you can request a cashout via the <code>/referral</code> menu. Withdrawals are processed to your registered bank account or e-wallet. Processing usually takes 1–3 business days.
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Account Management -->
    <div class="faq-category">
      <div class="faq-category-title">Account Management</div>
      <div class="accordion">

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-btn" onclick="toggle(this)">
            How do I change my language or settings?
            <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            In the web app, go to <strong>Settings</strong> from the sidebar. You can change your display language (Indonesian, English, Russian, Chinese) and other preferences. In the bot, use the <code>/profile</code> command to access your settings.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-btn" onclick="toggle(this)">
            How long are my videos stored?
            <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Videos are stored for <strong>30 days</strong> after generation. You can download them any time within this window using the secure download link. After 30 days, videos are automatically deleted — make sure to save important videos to your device.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-btn" onclick="toggle(this)">
            How do I delete my account?
            <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            To delete your account and all associated data, contact support via <a href="https://t.me/codergaboets">@codergaboets</a> or use the <code>/support</code> command in the bot. Include your Telegram username in the request. Account deletion is processed within 7 business days.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-btn" onclick="toggle(this)">
            I have a different question. How do I get help?
            <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Use the <code>/support</code> command in the bot to open a support ticket or chat directly with the support team. You can also reach us on Telegram at <a href="https://t.me/codergaboets">@codergaboets</a>.
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>&copy; 2026 BK Vilona AI &mdash; All rights reserved.</p>
  <p style="margin-top:8px">
    <a href="https://t.me/<%= botUsername %>">Telegram Bot</a> &middot;
    <a href="/app">Web App</a> &middot;
    <a href="/faq">FAQ</a> &middot;
    <a href="/terms">Terms &amp; Conditions</a> &middot;
    <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> &middot;
    <a href="https://t.me/codergaboets">Support</a>
  </p>
</footer>

<script>
  function toggle(btn) {
    const item = btn.closest('.accordion-item');
    const isOpen = item.classList.contains('open');
    // Close all
    document.querySelectorAll('.accordion-item.open').forEach(el => el.classList.remove('open'));
    // Open clicked unless it was already open
    if (!isOpen) item.classList.add('open');
  }
</script>

</body>
</html>
